title: Nice affordable house
posting_body: ['This is a small 4-BR house and it is priced accordingly', 'Mostly wood floors.', 'Central AC.', 'New paint throughout.', 'One bath.', 'Laundry', 'No garage, but there is a storage shed.', 'Tenant pays all utilities.', 'Available to move on August 20.', 'The first showing is on Thursday, August 4, at noon.', 'Must call Tony at', 'show contact info', 'an hour ahead of time to confirm the showing.', 'With questions about terms and qualifications, please send an email or text or call Alex at', 'show contact info', '.', 'We accept rental assistance.', 'Acceptance criteria are listed on the rental application, except minimum gross income is $4850 if there is no rental assistance.', 'Management complies with Minneapolis Code of Ordinances / Title 12 - HOUSING / CHAPTER 244.', '- MAINTENANCE CODE / ARTICLE XVI.', '- RENTAL DWELLING LICENSES  / 244.2030.', '- Applicant screening criteria for prospective tenants.', 'Application fee is $30, or $45 if lived out of state within last 5 years.', "Pets are accepted with additional refundable deposit; for aggressive breeds must have a proof of renter's insurance with liability coverage before move-in.", 'For mid- and large-size dogs, additional rent $15/mo.', "For cats and small dogs, add'l rent $10/mo.", 'Keywords: North Minneapolis']
